    summary: "The Blue Yeti is the most popular streaming mic for a reason — it sounds good out of the box and the four pickup patterns handle solo streaming, interviews, and podcasts. Just use it in cardioid mode, get it close to your mouth (6-8 inches), and add a noise gate in OBS."
  },
  {
    name: "Elgato Wave:3",
    badge: "Best Mid-Range Mic",
    price: 150,
    type: "USB Condenser",
