    cons: ["Cardioid only — no pattern switching", "Needs boom arm for best results", "Wave Link is Windows/Mac only"],
    summary: "The Wave:3 is the best USB mic for streamers. Clipguard is a hardware-level limiter that prevents your audio from clipping when you shout — invaluable for gaming. Wave Link gives you a virtual mixer with separate audio channels for game, music, chat, and mic. The 24-bit capture sounds noticeably cleaner than 16-bit mics."
  },
  {
    name: "Shure SM7B",
    badge: "Best Pro Mic",
    price: 400,
    type: "XLR Dynamic",
    pattern: "Cardioid",
    sampleRate: "Depends on interface",
