    summary: "The SM7B is the mic you see on every major streamer's desk for a reason — it makes your voice sound like a radio host. As a dynamic mic, it rejects background noise far better than any condenser, so your mechanical keyboard and PC fans disappear. You need an XLR interface (Focusrite Scarlett 2i2) and possibly a Cloudlifter for enough gain."
  }
