    summary: "If you game at 4K144 and refuse to compromise on passthrough quality, the Live Gamer Ultra 2.1 is the only external capture card with HDMI 2.1. Most streamers don't need this, but if you have a PS5 Pro or high-end PC pushing 4K, it future-proofs your setup."
  }
];

const lighting = [
