      <h2>Lighting</h2>
      <p>Lighting is the most underrated part of a streaming setup. A $60 webcam with good lighting looks better than a $900 camera in a dark room. Start with one light source and upgrade to two for shadow-free illumination.</p>
      <div class="table-wrapper">
        <table class="sortable-table">
          <thead>
            <tr>
