      <h2>OBS Settings Guide</h2>
      <p>These are the recommended OBS Studio settings for each budget tier. The most important settings are encoder, bitrate, and resolution — get these right and everything else is fine-tuning.</p>
      <div class="table-wrapper">
        <table class="sortable-table">
          <thead>
