          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <p>The "recommended" column accounts for concurrent gaming traffic. If you're playing an online game while streaming, your upload needs to handle both the stream bitrate and game data. Budget at least 50% headroom above your stream bitrate.</p>

